    "body": "Updating the neovim recipe to:\r\n- Add version 0.4.4\r\n- Fix build errors for github branches master and stable\r\n  - Lua version was set at 5.1:5.2, but neovim only allows Lua version 5.1, not 5.2\r\n  - Dependency versions were picked incorrectly for labels stable and master\r\n  - For centos7, a newer version of git was required. Added as a build dependency\r\n  - For version 0.2.0, building failed due to issues with dependency libvterm\r\n\r\nUpdating libvterm:\r\n- Version 0.0.0 was pointing to the incorrect file (typo?)\r\n- Version 0.1.4 was added",
